  <h2 id="combat_data_packs">Grind Shipyard EXP MANUALLY</h2>
  <HR />
  <p>
    Combat Data packs should NOT be used for completing the EXP grind in
    <WikiLink page="Research#Shipyard">Shipyard</WikiLink>. Instead, they should
    be used in the
    <WikiLink page="Shops#Prototype Shop">Prototype Shop</WikiLink>
    to buy Gear Blueprints.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <p>
        The Gear acquired through this method could take upwards of up to
        <b>3+ months</b> to get through normal means, not to mention the opportunity
        cost of doing Research on other seasons.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        The EXP grind takes a maximum of <b>1-2 weeks</b> when committing to it,
        even for mid-game players.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <br />

  <p>
    For more information about Research, check out the
    <b
      ><a
        href="research"
        target="_self"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        title="Research Guide">Research Guide</a
      ></b
    >.
  </p>
